[One wonders if this newly confirmed case is part of the extended family cluster in Hufoof that has been reported earlier (see MERS-CoV (43): Saudi Arabia, new cases 20150511.3355644) or if this was related to contact in the healthcare environment. More information on the likely transmission mode would be greatly appreciated.

A map showing the location of the current reported case can be found at the source URL. - Mod.MPP]

